Iran has imposed sanctions on 51 Americans while their proxy militias continue to attack American troops in the Middle East. Iranian officials have also threatened to carry out terror operations in the United States and around the world. The United States is determined to protect its citizens, both current and former. Despite political disagreements, Americans are united in their resolve against threats. The US will collaborate with allies and partners to deter and respond to any Iranian attacks. Iran will face severe consequences if it attacks any US nationals, including the 51 individuals named in the sanctions.